  "title": "Rat Academy 2 - Gnaw and Order",
  "description": "The last two rats in Alberta are back, and this time, they’re serving justice. When Fingers and Shrimp are evicted from their Whyte Avenue alley, they’re forced to search for a new three-walled haven. Will they love it? List it? Meet their maker in the jaws of the law? You’ll have to come to the show to find out.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Dayna Lea Hoffmann and Katie Yoner<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Joseph McManus<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Katie Yoner, Dayna Lea Hoffmann<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Claire Sonmor (Set/Props Design), Whittyn Jason (Lighting Design), Meegan Sweet (Costume Design), Liv McRobbie (Sound Design)<br/><strong>Stage Manager</strong>: Abby McDougall<br/>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/the_rat_academy",
  "plain_language": "The last two rats in Alberta, Fingers and Shrimp, fight to stay in the rat-free province after being kicked out of their home in this hilarious story about a trial.",
